Package gr.aueb.dmst.onepercent.programming

Class ContainerModel

java.lang.Object
gr.aueb.dmst.onepercent.programming.ContainerModel
public class ContainerModel extends Object
Class: ContainerModel class is used to create a model of a container. It is used in ContainerMonitor class to print the information about the containers. Its purpose is modeling the container and making it easier to print the information about it.
